{"tid":1902604,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"Travis Scott x Nike SB Dunk Low Nike 官方發售為 2 月 29 日","createTime":"2020-02-28T12:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T00:11:10.000Z","uid":350095,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5817c18870dac0c54946787b6e62a9e39795f3b8","tid":1902604,"uid":350095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T12:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FtSLUT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FtSLUT.jpg&h=483fa19f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nNike 經典鞋款 SB Dunk Low 在本月迎來與人氣歌手 Travis Scott 打造之最新聯名鞋款「Cactus Jack」，過去曾為大家率先曝光高清圖輯，以深藍色、米色、棕色等配色建構，加入變形蟲圖樣以及格紋呈現更多層次感，招牌的厚實鞋舌與鞋墊處皆注入 Cactus Jack 字樣，鞋帶部分則採用類似粗麻繩的質料，而 Swoosh Logo 則分別以一黑一米白的配色作配搭。<br />\n<br />\n驚喜的是，Travis Scott x Nike SB Dunk Low「Cactus Jack」全新聯名系列意外於 Travis Scott 個人線上商城突襲發售，並順勢推出一系列的滑板周邊系列，更順勢公開了特製的鞋盒設計。此外 Travis Scott 亦找來了 Evan Mock，Alex Midler 與 Ishod Wair 等知名滑板手演繹該鞋，透過極為復刻的影像風格做呈現。<br />\n<br />\n目前聯名鞋款與部分周邊已經售罄，有興趣的讀者不妨點此前進商城，<span style=\"color: red;\">Nike 官方發售為 2 月 29 日，建議售價 $150 美金。</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知香港官方發售係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e2f1f7f14bb6790abaa420568710a5497eac6b","tid":1902604,"uid":9975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:37:21.000Z","msg":"9000@1<br />\n<br />\ntg: sellkicks"},{"pid":"fd035ea50078c9eda66ec216f7ac6a275f812233","tid":1902604,"uid":15047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5817c18870dac0c54946787b6e62a9e39795f3b8","tid":1902604,"uid":350095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T12:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FtSLUT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FtSLUT.jpg&h=483fa19f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nNike 經典鞋款 SB Dunk Low 在本月迎來與人氣歌手 Travis Scott 打造之最新聯名鞋款「Cactus Jack」，過去曾為大家率先曝光高清圖輯，以深藍色、米色、棕色等配色建構，加入變形蟲圖